          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-zinc-800 text-sm text-zinc-600">
        Built with Astro, FastAPI, and PostgreSQL. Powered by TMDB.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
